# 2D (feature.2d)

## Package

`com.unity.feature.2d` — 2D Animation, Tilemap, Sprite, Aseprite, Pixel Perfect, etc.

## Policy

- 2D gameplay lives under `Assets/Game/Art/` (sprites, tilemaps) and `Scenes/Levels/`
- **Camera**: Cinemachine with **orthographic** lens on `CinemachineCamera` (see `unity-cinemachine.mdc`)
- Physics: 2D colliders/rigidbodies; no mixed 3D physics unless intentional

## MCP

- **core** (MCP-first): scenes, sprites, tilemaps via `manage_asset`, `manage_gameobject`, `manage_components`
- **probuilder** not for 2D tile workflows
- **vfx**: VFX Graph only (strict policy in `unity-vfx.mdc`) — validate 2D sorting with URP

## Default template

Starter `Game.unity` is **3D URP**; 2D projects add orthographic camera + 2D scenes as needed.
